{"tid":2277194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"重傷外賣員情況好轉，foodpanda回應「乞兒保險」模稜兩可","createTime":"2020-11-08T09:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T10:30:02.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16abe32c28ec920b82a870637adfd340f5da5865","tid":2277194,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"47歲foodpanda外賣員Taddy日前在沙田送外賣途中遇車禍重傷，留醫4日，今日情況由危殆轉為嚴重，現時不用依靠儀器，可自行呼吸，但仍未清醒。據家人稱，Taddy臉部表情亦較昨日稍為輕鬆，似熟睡「冇噚日咁痛苦」。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生後，有foodpanda外賣員指公司為自僱人士買的團體意外保險賠償額極低，住院賠償僅50元一天，上限15日，意外身故亦只得10萬元賠償，慨嘆「同畀乞兒冇分別」。foodpanda回應表示， 一直非常重視送遞員的安全，亦會為每位送遞員提供免費的自選意外保險，以及身故賠償。除了住院開支外，保險範圍亦涵蓋殘疾保障及醫療開支。但未有正面回應員工所指的團體意外保險賠償額極低的問題，《蘋果》正向foodpanda查詢有關免費的自選意外保險，與員工所指的團體意外保險是否不同。<br />\n<br />\n更多內文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201108/IKKL4MUGCJH5DMTR2XBOZUXVCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201108%2FIKKL4MUGCJH5DMTR2XBOZUXVCU%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq784e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=01b4920d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201108%2FIKKL4MUGCJH5DMTR2XBOZUXVCU%2F&h=f1688d32\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201108/IKKL4MUGCJH5DMTR2XBOZUXVCU/</a>"},{"pid":"7404bbe797a9413ac94b68c9607cba8b68af3846","tid":2277194,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"上一個post <br />\n<br />\n事源<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2273991/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2273991/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c3ffb3ccefeb2744b2447cb1ba242bef31e41d94","tid":2277194,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"除左熊貓份保應該仲有7人車份保喎<br />\n雖然份保同無無分別<br />\n不過7人車份保應該有幾百萬"},{"pid":"d9fad42cb62ea66d27928138611b7d25d35c4df6","tid":2277194,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c3ffb3ccefeb2744b2447cb1ba242bef31e41d94","tid":227719